Project: Computer Graphics

Tanmay Desai and Jhansi Saketa BV
Department of Computer Science


Key bindings
  
  0 		 Reset theta and phi
  r		 Rain
  l		 Snow
  h		 Hail
  arrows     Change view angle
  
  ESC        Exit

  Things to look at:  
  Life-like scene, texturing, changing seasons, moving objects

  Things to do:
  First-person view, collecting and melting of ice, street lights, day and night.

  Code we reused:
  We used rain code and customized accordingly for our project and made snow and hail out of it.
